2.00	40_More_Reasons_to_Hate_Us	40 More Reasons to Hate Us	40 More Reasons to Hate Us is the third album by Anal Cunt, recorded after their Japanese Tour in June 1995 and released on March 26, 1996 by Earache Records. The name of the album reflected the notoriety that the band had achieved due to their controversial song titles and lyrics, as well as their friendly relationships with racist music groups such as Vaginal Jesus.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/83/40MoreReasonstoHateUs.jpg/220px-40MoreReasonstoHateUs.jpg
